<html>
  <head>
    <title>My Email Template</title>
    <style type="text/css">
      p { margin: 0; color: #26262C;}
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
      <tr>
        <td align="center" bgcolor="#EAF0F3" style="padding: 30px 0;">
          <table
            border="0"
            cellpadding="0"
            cellspacing="0"
            width="600"
            style="width: 100%; max-width: 600px;"
          >
            <tr>
              <td align="left" style="padding: 20px" bgcolor="#fff">
                <img src="cid:alike_logo" alt="alike_logo" />
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td bgcolor="#fff" align="center">
                <img src="cid:mailer" alt="mailer" width="250" />
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td bgcolor="#fff" align="center">
                <p style="font-size: 20px; font-weight: bold">
                  이메일 인증번호:
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td bgcolor="#fff" align="center" style="padding-top: 4px;">
                <table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="8">
                  <tr>
                    {{#each code}}
                      <td
                        style="
                        width: 32px;
                        height: 32px;
                        vertical-align: middle;
                        border-radius: 8px;
                      "
                        bgcolor="#EAF0F3"
                        align="center"
                      >
                        <p style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 500;">
                          {{this}}
                        </p>
                      </td>
                    {{/each}}
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td
                bgcolor="#fff"
                align="center"
                style="padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 60px"
              >
                <p style="font-size: 12px">회원가입을 위한 인증번호 입니다.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 12px">
                  위 인증번호를 입력하여 인증을 완료해주세요.
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td bgcolor="#fff" style="padding: 20px" align="center">
                <hr />
                <p style="font-size: 12px">본 메일은 발신전용 메일입니다.</p>
                <p style="font-size: 12px">&copy; 2023 Alike</p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>